description: Researchers say chagas disease can cause mild flu-like symptoms at first, but it is potentially deadly. Cases have been reported in eight states.

description: Brittany Bertoul and her dad, Giorgio, were about to do the traditional father/daughter dance when a video of them dancing to "Beauty and the Beast" more than 28 years ago appeared on a giant screen.
title: Bride and Her Dad Recreate Decades-Old Video Dance Moment #shorts

author: Inside Edition
description: Ashley King warns travelers after a methanol-tainted cocktail in Bali left her blind. Her incident occurred at 18 when she and a friend were traveling in the Indonesian province. They went out for drinks, and Ashley unknowingly drank a beverage that almost killed her. After getting rushed to the hospital and fighting for her life, she was told that her eyesight would never return. "It felt like a death sentence," she told Inside Edition Digital's Andrea Swindall.
title: Actress Warns Travelers After Methanol-Tainted Cocktail in Bali Left Her Blind
